&"text": "🥳",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"200": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "200",
&"next_id": "201",
&"text": "She seemed like a really nice person 😊",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"201": {
&"character": "Mabel",
&"id": "201",
&"next_id": "202",
&"text": "Oh hmm, well the guy with the camera was nice too even though he seemed shy",
