raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Day2 mission complete
Player: Welcome back!
Player: How was your day??
Mabel: Honestly, EXHAUSTINGG
Mabel: I feel like my body is being pushed to its limits 😩
Mabel: It's like every class I go to, I'm just getting totally stretched out from head to toe before getting to relax for 10 minutes
- Hang in there!
	Player: Hang in there!
	Mabel: Thanks babe 🥰
- I'd like to see that [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: I'd like to see that
	Mabel: Hmm? See what?
	Mabel: Them putting me on a rack? 😂
	Player: Something like that 😆
Mabel: Oh!!
Mabel: I made a new friend today omg!
Mabel: I almost forgot to tell you
Player: 🥳
Mabel: 😊
Player: Student in your class?
Mabel: Not exactly!
Mabel: She wasn't a student in my class buuut
Mabel: After class, Prof Suzanna called me up to ask if everything was okay 🥰
Player: Nice of her!!
Mabel: She's so kind omg 🥺
Mabel: Then this girl walked in!
Mabel: My professor introduced us
Mabel: Okay so her name is Naomi!
Mabel: She said she was in photography club, looking for members
Mabel: Ms Suzanna called her in because she said I might have difficulty socializing in a boys only class on my first year 😆
- She's got a point!
	Player: She's got a point!
	Mabel: Right? Anyway!
- Why not try socializing with them? [#distrust]
	Player: Why not try socializing with them?
	Mabel: I mean... I guess I could if I really tried but...
	Mabel: Thought: They give me really weird looks
	Mabel: Thought: I think one of them was drooling
	Mabel: Thought: Did he want to steal my lunch or something?
	Mabel: I'd... rather not if I don't have to 🙂
Mabel: I was like wow you went all that way? 🥺 For me?
Mabel: I might have cried if I wasn't so shy of meeting a new girl 😇
Mabel: Anyway! We had lunch together and she asked me about everything 😊
Mabel: At first I gave like one word answers, omg
Mabel: I must have been so boring to talk to 😓
Mabel: Then after like an hour
Mabel: She was listening to me ramble!
do social_post(\"erikas_search\")
Mabel: Kind of like when you do 🥰
Player: Kind of like now?
Mabel: Exactly!!
Mabel: Wait I mean no!
Player: 😁
Mabel: Omg stop 😆
Mabel: I don't think she disliked it
Mabel: Anyway she said she had some errands to run and some work to do but she gave me her Social
Mabel: But she wanted to take a picture before she left
Player: At this rate, you're gonna become a celebrity
Mabel: I don't like attention 🥹 it scares me
Mabel: But I'm happy I made a new friend!
Player: See? Friends are good!
Mabel: Fiiine you were right 🙃
if Story.mabel_trust <= 40
	Mabel: But omg, I need to call Nina soon too
	Mabel: She said she wants to share the juiciest gossip ever 😅
	Mabel: I'm a gossip girl now babe 😆🥹
Player: 😂
Player: Do you have the picture you guys took?
Mabel: Can't get enough of me huh? 😁🩷
- Never [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: Never
	Mabel: 🥰
- I want to see who's cuter 😌
	Player: I want to see who's cuter 😌
	Mabel: Pick me pick me 🥹
	Mabel: 🤭
Mabel: But yeah
Mabel: Here!
if Story.has_flag(\"CuteOutfit\")
	Mabel: img: mabel/44
	Mabel: Omg I just realized I'm wearing the dress you picked out for me
	Mabel: I look like a doll next to a real college student 🥹
	Mabel: She looks so smart and cool
	Mabel: And I look like I'm visiting my big sis or something
elif Story.has_flag(\"ModernOutfit\")
	Mabel: img: mabel/46
	Mabel: Wow look at us!
	Mabel: This outfit was perfect for today omg
	Mabel: I feel like a smart college student hehe
elif Story.has_flag(\"HotOutfit\")
	Mabel: img: mabel/48
	Mabel: Omg this is soooo embarassing
	Mabel: I totally look like one of those club girls next to her 🥹
Player: Looking good!
Mabel: Me or her? 👀
Mabel: Actually don't answer that
Mabel: I'm too tired for your teasing me right now 😂
Player: Who took the picture?
Mabel: Oh! Right, there was a guy with her
Mabel: I didn't notice him at first!!
Mabel: He was really quiet and I just thought he was another student
Mabel: We even had lunch and he was just sort of in the background 😅
Mabel: It was funny cause he was quite tall 😅 Like how didn't I notice him at all??
Player: Oh interesting 🤔
Mabel: Isn't it?
Mabel: He had a camera with him and he was took the pictures
Mabel: Naomi was so sweet to him but he was all shy quiet and blushy
Mabel: I think she didn't want to push him
Mabel: But that's when I kind of realized that they might be dating
Player: You didn't ask?
Mabel: No! I didn't want to sound like I'm assuming anything
Mabel: But I wish you were following me around like he was following her 🥹
Mabel: I seriously need you by my side always
Mabel: I could imagine it being her boyfriend 😊
- Was he cute? [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Was he cute?
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: 😳
	Mabel: Thought: Now that I think about it.. uhm, yeah a little
	Mabel: Uhm... uhh ehhh
	Mabel: N-no?
	Player: Maaabes? 😏
	Mabel: Don't you \"Mabes\" me!
	Mabel: Maybe a little!
	Mabel: But what's point of asking that kind of question when we're together and you're my one and only 🥹
	Mabel: Thought: Oh my god I am SO corny and lame
	Mabel: What if I asked you if Naomi was cute??
	- I'd be honest about it and say yes
		Player: I'd be honest about it and say yes
		Mabel: Uhm... okay well
		Mabel: I don't think we ever talked about something like that
		Mabel: But is this normal to talk about?
		Mabel: Because I feel a little jealous that you said that 🥹
		Mabel: But I also felt a bit of relief when I spoke my mind
		- You can share anything with me! [#trust]
			set Story.mabel_trust += 1
			Player: You can share anything with me!
			Mabel: Even if... if I uhm..
			Mabel: If I find other guys attractive?
			Mabel: That's interesting, do you really want to know stuff like that?
			Mabel: 😳
			Player: I did say \"anything\"
			Mabel: Okay 🙈 ..fine
			Mabel: To be totally clear though, I don't uhm...
			Mabel: Like 99.99% of guys are not attractive to me
			Mabel: He was just a little bit of an exception
			Mabel: So that's my honest answer 😇
			Mabel: Besides they are probably boyfriend girlfriend so it doesn't even mean anything
			Player: You could be right about that
			do heart(0)
		- Maybe we should keep our secrets actually [#distrust]
			set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
			Player: Maybe we should keep our secrets actually
			Mabel: Huh!?
			do heart(0)
			Mabel: You say that like you're hiding things from me 😑
			Mabel: Babe you're not cheating on me are you?? 🥺😭
			Player: What!? Of course not!
			Mabel: Okay good 😊
			Mabel: And you know I'd never ever never do anything like that to you right?
			Player: Of course 😊
			Mabel: Thought: I couldn't even bear the thought of another boy
	- Those girls from the sorority were a bit more my type [#distrust]
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
		Player: Those girls from the sorority were a bit more my type
		Mabel: You mean like Nina??
		do heart(0)
		Mabel: You like.. crazy kind of hairstyles and outfits?
		Player: Something like that 😶‍🌫️
		Mabel: Wow... I didn't really expect that 😅
		Mabel: Thought: Maybe I should learn a thing or two from them?
		Mabel: I guess maybe our tiny town was a bit boring for you
		- Wasn't it boring for you too? [#lust]
			set Story.mabel_desire += 1
			Player: Wasn't it boring for you too?
			Player: Don't you feel a bit more 'free' here?
			Mabel: I... never.. 🤔
			Mabel: I never really thought about that 😳
			Mabel: I mean I guess I can kind of do whatever I want but I don't even know what there is to do
			Player: The fun is finding out 😁
			Mabel: Maybe you're right
			Mabel: Maybe there's some experience that's out there waiting for me hehe 🥰
			Mabel: Gotta be positive even though I seriously miss home
		- Just a little
			Player: Just a little
			Mabel: I miss the little things
			Mabel: I feel like there's too much going on here!
			Mabel: I'm usually smiley back at home but now I just feel like this all the time
- What did you guys talk about?
	Player: What did you guys talk about?
	Player: Anything interesting?
	Mabel: Just friendly chit-chat! 
	Mabel: Like the weather might get cold soon and stuff
	Mabel: Thought: And Naomi had such a beautiful voice too omg
	Mabel: Thought: I didn't want her to stop talking
	Mabel: She seemed like a really nice person 😊
	Mabel: Oh hmm, well the guy with the camera was nice too even though he seemed shy
	Mabel: He showed me his camera reel and some of the pictures were really pretty!
	Player: Photography guy have a name?
	Mabel: Yeah I think he told me buuuut I forgot 😅
	Player: Classic Mabes! 😆
	Mabel: Hey it was like too many friendly people suddenly appearing okay!
	Mabel: Was a bit 😵‍💫
	Mabel: But yeah that was it!
	Mabel: Not too eventful but it was nice 😇
	Player: Glad to hear that
Mabel: Anyway maybe I'll text Naomi later 🤩
Mabel: It's getting late now 🥱
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Mabel: img: mabel/49
	Mabel: Look how yawny your girl is 😊
	Player: Uhm Mabel?
	Mabel: Hmm?
	Mabel: What
	Player: Your shirt
	Mabel: OMG!
	Mabel: I can't delete it now 😭
	Mabel: Can you delete it? 🥺😩
	Mabel: How did I not notice!?
	Player: You look nice though 👀
	Mabel: I'm soooo embarrassed 🙃
	Mabel: Okay byeee good night 😭
else: 
	Mabel: img: mabel/50
	Mabel: Look how yawny your girl is 😊
	Player: Cute!!
	Mabel: 🥰
	Mabel: Good night boyfriend of mine 😘
	Player: Night Mabes ❤️
	Player: Sleep tight
	Mabel: Night, maybe I'll dream of you 🥰
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
